#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Proxies are programs running on a computer that acts a server on the network "
"you are connected to (whether by modem or other means). These programs "
"receive &HTTP; and &FTP; requests, retrieve the relevant files from the "
"internet, and pass them on to the client computer that made the requests."
msgstr ""
"Posredniki (proxy-ji) so programi, ki tečejo na računalniku, ki deluje kot "
"strežnik na omrežju, na katerega ste povezani (z modemom ali kako drugače). "
"Ti programi prejemajo zahteve &HTTP; in &FTP;, pridobijo ustrezne datoteke "
"iz interneta in jih pošljejo na odjemalčev računalnik, ki je ustvaril "
"zahtevo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have configured a proxy, &HTTP; and/or &FTP; requests are re-routed "
"through the computer that is acting as a proxy server. However, you can also "
"select specific hosts which should be contacted directly, rather than "
"through the proxy server. If you are on a local network, for example, access "
"to local hosts probably doesn't need to go through a proxy server."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste nastavili posrednika, so vse zahteve &HTTP; in/ali &FTP; preusmerjene "
"preko računalnika, ki predstavlja posredniški strežnik. Lahko pa izberete "
"določene gostitelje, s katerimi boste povezani neposredno namesto preko "
"posredniškega strežnika. Če ste na krajevnem omrežju, potem npr. dostop do "
"krajevnih gostiteljev ni potreben preko posredniškega strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should only need to configure a proxy server if your network "
"administrator requires it (if you are a dial-up user, that would be your "
"internet service provider or <acronym>ISP</acronym>). Otherwise, especially "
"if you are feeling a bit confused about this proxy business, but everything "
"seems to be fine with your internet connection, you don't need to change "
"anything."
msgstr ""
"Posredniški strežnik nastavite samo, če to zahteva vaš vzdrževalec omrežja "
"(če ste klicni uporabnik, bi bil to vaš ponudnik interneta ali <acronym>ISP</"
"acronym>). V nasprotnem primeru, posebno če ste glede posrednikov nekoliko "
"zmedeni, vaša internetna povezava pa deluje v redu, potem vam ni potrebno "
"ničesar spreminjati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that using proxy servers is optional, but has the benefit or "
"advantage of giving you faster access to data on the internet."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo vedite, da je uporaba posredniških strežnikov neobvezna. Prednost pa "
"je v hitrejšemu dostopu do podatkov na internetu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are uncertain whether or not you need to use a proxy server to "
"connect to the internet, please consult with your internet service "
"provider's setup guide or your system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Če niste prepričani glede uporabe posredniškega strežnika za dostop do "
"interneta, potem se obrnite na vašega ponudnika internetnih storitev ali "
"vašega sistemskega skrbnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Use</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporaba</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "No Proxy"
msgstr "Brez posrednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if you do <emphasis>not</emphasis> want to use a proxy "
"server and connect to the Internet directly."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če <emphasis>ne</emphasis> želite uporabljati "
"posredniškega strežnika in želite uporabljati neposredno povezavo z "
"internetom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have decided to use a proxy, you have several methods to configure "
"the settings for it."
msgstr ""
"Če ste se odločili za uporabo posredniškega strežnika, potem imate na voljo "
"več načinov, kako skonfigurirati njegove nastavitve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect proxy configuration automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznaj datoteko za konfiguracijo posrednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if you want the proxy setup configuration script file to "
"be automatically detected and downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če se naj nastavitvena skriptna datoteka posrednika "
"samodejno zazna in naloži."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option only differs from the next choice in that it <emphasis>does not</"
"emphasis> require you to supply the location of the configuration script "
"file. Instead, it will be automatically downloaded using <quote>Web Proxy "
"Auto-Discovery</quote> (<acronym>WPAD</acronym>) protocol."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost se od naslednje loči samo v tem, da <emphasis>ne zahteva</"
"emphasis> navedbo lokacije nastavitvene skriptne datoteke. Namesto tega bo "
"samodejno prenesena z uporabo protokola  <quote>Web Proxy Auto-Discovery</"
"quote> (<acronym>WPAD</acronym>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use proxy auto configuration URL:"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznaj skriptno datoteko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if your proxy support is provided through a script file "
"located at a specific address. You can then enter the address in the "
"location text box, or use the <guiicon>folder</guiicon> icon to browse to it."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če se podpora vašemu posredniku izvaja preko skriptne "
"datoteke na določenem naslovu. Njen naslov lahko vnesete v polje za lokacijo "
"ali uporabite ikono z <guiicon>mapo</guiicon> da jo najdete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use system proxy configuration:"
msgstr "Uporabi sistemsko konfiguracijo posrednika:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some systems are setup with $<envar>HTTP_PROXY</envar> to allow graphical as "
"well as non-graphical applications to share the same proxy configuration "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri sistemi so postavljeni z $<envar>HTTP_PROXY</envar>, da si grafični "
"in besedilni programi delijo iste nastavitvene informacije posrednika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you know this applies to you, select this option and click on the "
"<guibutton>Auto Detect</guibutton> button to provide the environment "
"variable names used to set the address of the proxy server(s)."
msgstr ""
"Če veste, da je to pomembno za vas, izberite to možnost in kliknite na gumb "
"<guibutton>Samodejno Zaznaj</guibutton>, kjer boste podali imena okoljskih "
"spremenljivk, uporabljenih za nastavitev naslovov posredniških strežnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Exceptions:</guilabel> field enter the environment "
"variable, &eg; $<envar>NO_PROXY</envar>, used to store the addresses of "
"sites for which the proxy server should not be used."
msgstr ""
"V polje <guilabel>Izjeme:</guilabel> vnesite okoljsko spremenljivko, &eg; "
"$<envar>NO_PROXY</envar>, katero se uporablja za shranjevanje naslovov "
"spletnih strani , za katere naj posredniški strežnik ne bo uporabljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Show the value of the environment variables</guilabel> to show "
"the value of an environment variable instead of its name. However it is not "
"possible to edit the values of environment variables in this module."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Prikaži vrednost okoljske spremenljivke</guilabel>, da "
"prikažete vrednost okoljske spremenljivke namesto njenega imena. Ni pa "
"mogoče urejati vrednosti okoljskih spremenljivk v tem modulu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use manually specified proxy configuration:"
msgstr "Uporabi ročno navedeno skriptno datoteko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The complete addressing information for the proxy includes both the Internet "
"address and a port number. You should enter these into the relevant text "
"boxes. Check <guilabel>Use this proxy server for all protocols</guilabel> to "
"copy the addresses and port of the &HTTP; proxy server into all other proxy "
"fields, in order to help save some typing."
msgstr ""
"Celotna informacija za naslavljanje posrednika vključuje internetni naslov "
"IP in številko vrat. To vnesite v ustrezna vnosna polja. Označite "
"<guilabel>Uporabi ta posredniški strežnik z vse protokole</guilabel>, da "
"skopirate naslove in vrata &HTTP; posredniških strežnikov v vsa druga polja "
"za posrednike, da si prihranite nekaj tipkanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exceptions:"
msgstr "Izjeme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a comma separated list of hostnames or ip addresses that should be "
"excluded from using the above proxy settings. If you want to exclude all "
"hosts for a given domain, then simply enter the domain name preceded by a "
"dot. For example, to exclude all hostnames for kde.org, enter <userinput>."
"kde.org</userinput>. Wildcard characters such as <userinput>*</userinput> or "
"<userinput>?</userinput> are not supported and will have no effect. "
"Additionally, you can also enter IP addresses, &eg; 127.0.0.1 and IP "
"addresses with a subnet, &eg; 192.168.0.1/24."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite seznam imen gostiteljev ali IP naslovov ločen z vejico, ki jih "
"izključujete iz uporabljanja zgornjih nastavitev posrednika. Če to želite "
"izključiti vse gostitelje za določeno domeno, enostavno vnesite ime domene s "
"piko na začetku, npr. da izključite vsa imena gostiteljev za kde.org, "
"vnesite <userinput>.kde.org</userinput>. Nadomestni znaki, kot so "
"<userinput>*</userinput> ali <userinput>?</userinput>, niso podprti in ne "
"bodo imeli nobenega učinka. Prav tako lahko vnesete IP naslove, &eg; "
"127.0.0.1 in IP naslove z masko podomrežja, &eg; 192.168.0.1/24."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also choose <guilabel>Use proxy settings only for addresses in the "
"Exceptions list</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi možnost <guilabel>Uporabi nastavitve posrednika le za "
"vnose v Seznam Izjem</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to reverse the use of the exception list, &ie; the proxy "
"servers will only be used when the requested &URL; matches one of the "
"addresses listed here."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, da obrnete uporabo seznama izjem. To pomeni, da bodo "
"posredniški strežniki uporabljeni samo, če se zahtevan &URL; ujema z enim od "
"tukaj navedenih naslovov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is useful if all you need is a proxy to access a few specific "
"sites, for example, an internal intranet. If you have more complex "
"requirements you might want to use a configuration script."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je koristna, če potrebujete posrednika za dostop do samo "
"nekaterih strani, npr. za notranji intranet. Če imate bolj zahtevne potrebe, "
"potem uporabite nastavitveni skript."

